r><bibl><ref type="bibl" target="#src_Gurdž._Wadž."/><biblScope>35</biblScope></bibl></example><example><quote>byrcæj axawʒynæ</quote><tr xml:lang="ru"><q>ты упадешь с обрыва</q></tr><tr xml:lang="en"><q>you will fall from the steep</q></tr></example></exampleGrp><etym xml:lang="ru">Восходит к *%ibṛšti%i- (как <ref type="xr" target="#entry_arc"/> ‘копье’ к %iaršti%i-); cp. <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/> <w>bhrṣṭi-</w> <gloss><q>выступ</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/> <gloss><q>край</q></gloss></mentioned>, .</etym><etym xml:lang="en">It traces back to %i*bṛšti%i- (like <ref type="xr" target="#entry_arc"/> ‘lance’ to %iaršti%i-); cf. <mentioned xml:lang="sa"><lang/> <w>bhrṣṭi-</w> <gloss><q>ledge</q></gloss></mentioned><mentioned xml:lang="sa"><w/> <gloss><q>edge</q></gloss></mentioned>, .</etym></entry></body></text></TEI>